parameters: "Mishiro Usui's eyes will never again open."
Iron bars jut out of the ground.
It seems impossible to climb over them.
There's a lever on the wall.
The lever has already been activated.
Gold ingots of impressive thickness shine radiantly.
Mishiro checked for traps, then picked up the gold.
An old book rests on top of the desk.
With a quick read of the book,
it turns out to be a manual on using lamps.
Mishiro learned how to adjust the wick of her \i[272]\c[2]Lantern\c[0],
and can adjust its intensity with something that makes fire.
Adjusting the \i[272]\c[2]Lantern\c[0] can be done from the menu.
Iron bars jut out of the ground.
It seems impossible to climb over them.
